    <div class="collapse-content" id="collapse">
      <p>Step 1: Take a glass waste bin from the storage room.</p>
      <p>Step 2: Place the bin in a designated location for glass waste disposal.</p>
      <p>Step 3: Place an absorbent pad at the bottom of the bin.</p>
      <p>Step 4: Place glass waste in the bin.</p>
      <p>Step 5: When the bin is full, replace the absorbent pad and dispose of the glass waste in the appropriate container.</p>
